Define Facet Scope. Sort added patterns in Scope Details included table

Open facet
Add pattern and rename patterns to "org.eclipse.Q1" and "org.eclipse.E1"
Click Sort button in annotation based inclusion table
Verify inclusion 
Save changes
Reopen facet
Verify inclusion 
